Fidociary

ABOUT

Fidociary is an investment platform that specializes in providing accessible, transparent opportunities for retail investors to invest in Real World Assets (RWA), primarily focused on global real estate markets. The platform stands out by providing a simple, one-click investment experience for global real estate, catering to those who seek better liquidity options for property owners and more affordable avenues into real estate investment.

SCOPE

  • Branding

INDUSTRY

FinTech

CHALLENGES

Invest today,
Build your Tomorrow

01

Simplifying Fidociary’s real estate investment platform into an easy-to-understand brand.

02

Communicating both trust and simplicity, ensuring the brand felt approachable without sacrificing credibility.

03

Differentiating Fidociary from established competitors while highlighting its unique value of low-entry investment in global real estate.

04

Creating a cohesive brand narrative that communicates Fidociary’s accessibility and transparency, while appealing to both novice and experienced real estate investors.

SOLUTION

Identity that takes you to the top

The brand identity for Fidociary was meticulously crafted to reflect trust, transparency, and modernity. Using a sophisticated color palette of purple and greys, the visual elements were designed to communicate the brand’s core values—approachability and professionalism. The focus was on creating a clean, streamlined identity that stood out in the real estate investment market. This identity was built to resonate with both experienced investors and those new to the space, ensuring Fidociary’s brand presence was strong and trustworthy.

The branding exercise will have a significant impact on Fidociary, positioning the brand as a beacon of trust and professionalism in the real estate investment space. By employing a modern palette of purple and greys, the brand identity will establish a sleek and approachable tone, appealing to both seasoned investors and newcomers alike.his well-crafted identity will not only elevate the brand but also instill confidence in potential investors, ensuring long-term growth and recognition.
